chipmunk.unlimited.feedback.revfeed

Class FeedActivity

  • java.lang.Object
    • FragmentActivity
      • chipmunk.unlimited.feedback.revfeed.FeedActivity

  • public class FeedActivity
extends FragmentActivity
    Activity displaying a FeedFragment. This Activity is used to display "uncommon" feeds, such as feeds for a single course or a single lecture. One, and only one of the following parameters must be passed in the spawning Intent. +----------------------+---------+--------+ | Parameter name | Type | Value | +----------------------+---------+--------+ | PARAM_SINGLE_COURSE | boolean | TRUE | | PARAM_SINGLE_LECTURE | boolean | TRUE | +----------------------+---------+--------+ If PARAM_SINGLE_COURSE is set, the following parameters must also be set: PARAM_COURSE_NAME String The name of the course. PARAM_COURSE_CODE String The HiG code of the course If PARAM_SINGLE_CODE is set, the following parameters must also be set: PARAM_LECTURE_HASH String The SHA1 of the lecture PARAM_ACTIONBAR_TITLE String The action bar title
